Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.99,0:00:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.66,0:00:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.41,0:00:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是谈论这种话题的季节了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.47,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够不去想自已不愿想起的事情就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.07,0:00:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的头脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.87,0:00:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不送给令大人巧克力了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.84,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 相对于每年都变得更大的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.95,0:00:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拿什么送给我才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 令大人每年也要送给你礼物吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.59,0:00:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大人与她的外表相反 内心相当的女孩子气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.80,0:00:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作糕点的手艺更是让专业人员都甘拜下风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也变好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.42,0:00:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用市面贩卖的巧克力大概是不行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.69,0:00:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要是巧克力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.73,0:00:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用其它的东西也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.83,0:00:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是亲手做的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在温暖着由乃同学的这些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.76,0:01:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是令大人亲手做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.02,0:01:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能给你做参考真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.54,0:01:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.47,0:01:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你想送给祥子大人的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我和祥子大人初次的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.03,0:01:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.63,0:01:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.94,0:01:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.70,0:01:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.46,0:01:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒缓的行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.40,0:03:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}吃惊的巧克力·前篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧 志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呀 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我至少情人节还是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.12,0:03:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月14日 瓦伦丁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.54,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是记念殉教的意大利圣人的节日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过与巧克力好像是没什么关系就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你不送给白蔷薇大人巧克力了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对志摩子同学来说也是初次的情人节吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想都没想过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.91,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能给你做参考真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 问我也是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很不凑巧既没有姐姐也没有妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起原来所想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节也许会是一个很麻烦的活动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没法依靠由乃同学与志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它人里该问谁才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要是一年级生呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.02,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.95,0:04:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是二年级生还是三年级生\n可也是体验过一年级生的生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 三年级生正忙于应付考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.81,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够问的人就只有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.19,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给姐姐的巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.35,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去年是送过 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.32,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想能够听听做一下参考就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个很简朴的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹心苦味巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以将制作方法写给你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没法成为参考啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我自满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做糕点上除了曾做过\n烤面圈的定型外其它什么都不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前途多难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾们的巧克力在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新闻部的情人节企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位花蕾将在校内藏起亲手做的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.79,0:05:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳 情况还很混乱 你稍微安静一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你特意来访 但我们无法协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.69,0:05:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想改善新闻部的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 这也是很能为一般学生们所接受的企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.24,0:05:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.33,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 将食物长时间存放就是一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且将巧克力堂堂正正地\n带进学校也不知是否行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 老师们也说了情人节就睁一只眼闭一只眼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.85,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单方面被强迫接受的礼物只是一种麻烦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.36,0:06:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说祥子大人不喜欢情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.81,0:06:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到全校里充满了巧克力的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说祥子大人也讨厌巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.07,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么如果改变宝物的话 能否同意参加这个企划呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.13,0:06:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将手写的情人节卡片藏起来 红色 黄色 白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.28,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来一开始就不是想要巧克力 而是盯着卡片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再把那些卡片做为附加奖的兑换卷如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附加奖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与花蕾们的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.06,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是山百合会主办的 那么我们就不能参加了是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 就是说只能让我以外的其它人与姐姐约会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对反对 绝对反对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将个人的私有时间商品化是不对的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.60,0:07:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 山百合会全员一致拒绝这个企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.26,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为由乃同学的竭力反对 这个企划被驳回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对新闻部的回答决定了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连黄蔷薇大人也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐们聚在一起下了命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就算不是心甘情愿也只有同意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟以前一样 头脑顽固呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了这样一个顽固脑袋作妹妹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是哪一位呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才希望你的头脑能变得稍微灵活一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.57,0:08:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和普通学生们的交流 不是很好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在选了佑巳作妹妹后 脸上的表情已经好看多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.96,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.88,0:08:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一回合 祥子大人的K.O.败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.04,0:08:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要说什么 你明白的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会协助新闻部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.67,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种向人施压的方式 不觉得太过份了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令也是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在和令说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.81,0:08:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望没有关系的人不要插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.62,0:08:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗 由乃越是认真就越会让姐姐干劲十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差得远呢 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回合 令大人与由乃同学放弃比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三回合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事 加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣大人的不战而胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳好像闷闷不乐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.95,0:09:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.73,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.14,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明祥子大人只要能向我笑一笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能感到安心的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢各位欣然允诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.66,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡片的隐藏地点\n应局限于学生们平常能出入的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.09,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对特定人员有利的教室或活动室 我认为应该排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～ 最差劲的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.73,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是花蕾的妹妹 我应该也能参加的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.82,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次活动 能否改为只有花蕾们参加企划呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.00,0:09:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.75,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 花蕾以外的人都能参加寻宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.89,0:10:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们两人来说 也不是件坏事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你们不想赌上那几百分之一的概率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到与姐姐们约会的机会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾们的妹妹们能参加的话 也可成为很好的话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了这种时候的杂活 才需要妹妹帮忙的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.25,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人一点都没想到要与我约会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.32,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我还有一个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.71,0:10:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在卡片的隐藏地点中加上蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐… 为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里本来是学生会议室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时蔷薇大人们被神圣化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不再靠近这里了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在毕业之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.01,0:10:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看蔷薇馆里普通学生们喧闹的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我的梦想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.57,0:11:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后的情人节里 将最好的一天作为礼物送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟总是焦虑不安的我不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓉子大人与祥子大人牢固地联系着彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会找到令的卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没什么信心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.27,0:11:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.29,0:11:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓姐妹 就是有只有身为姐妹才有的好处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为充分地理解对方的兴趣和嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.11,0:11:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以总能找到寻找卡片的线索吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.93,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在身边 很可能会不经意地透露出一些提示呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 是什么时候隐藏的从态度上就可以看出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.36,0:11:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好处的不是姐妹 而是由乃同学才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.91,0:11:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到情人节之前 这种情况会很常见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在蔷薇馆里也变得有点辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.11,0:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人成为红蔷薇大人后 会变得更忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.02,0:12:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 祥子大人与我的距离或许会变得更远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.81,0:12:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.79,0:12:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.37,0:12:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要成为姐姐的负担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让姐姐担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是花蕾们在那边交谈 让你感到不安了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天色已经这么暗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.93,0:12:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到不安并不是因为黑暗 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学 你真的什么也不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花蕾们准备把卡片放在哪里什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.93,0:13:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.71,0:13:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么提示也好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.59,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们也要参加活动 所以真的什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们去图书馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.69,0:13:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 以活泼为优点的佑巳同学竟会叹气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 对妹妹们来说现在是很不开心的状况了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.54,0:13:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑巳同学不去图书馆吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.04,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休时大家好像都去查有关巧克力的书了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人看起来很讨厌巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.80,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人在圣诞节\n可是吃了一大块圣诞巧克力蛋糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄蔷薇的花蕾亲手做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.33,0:13:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\n也就是只反感在情人节送巧克力这个风俗了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.43,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是哪一边 对我来说都是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.05,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在情人节送巧克力的乐趣消失无踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.84,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而喜欢的人又可能会与别人去约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒真是让人提不起劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.19,0:14:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蔷薇馆里也无容身之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里的话题又全都是情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能对你有所帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.24,0:14:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令的特制配方也在里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.56,0:14:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大人干劲十足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.45,0:14:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说\n大家常被其美少年般的外表所迷惑而未注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她其实真的是一个很爱照顾别人的好心人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.19,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 毕竟能和那个由乃同学好好相处了这么长时间嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么吃惊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.63,0:14:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.34,0:14:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.73,0:14:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是要商量关于情人节的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.04,0:14:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有什么事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人心情好像也很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就别在这儿闲聊浪费时间 快点回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.41,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子 别用那种口气说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.27,0:15:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我强把佑巳带来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.15,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 能顺道去菊组把这个交给由乃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.30,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把巧克力交给\N心情那么恶劣的祥子大人果然是太勉强了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在迷惑中到了情人节的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑情人节能成为我最好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.23,0:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.87,0:16:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 差不多也是合唱部的练习时间了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 反正大家还没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节看来很麻烦的样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.35,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对花蕾们的妹妹来说 特别是今年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.15,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.56,0:16:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也准备送给白蔷薇大人巧克力喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.56,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人节不正是适合传达心意的日子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明对白蔷薇大人做过失礼的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个越打越坚强的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为白蔷薇大人很体贴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不会拒绝收到的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 红蔷薇的花蕾可就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.03,0:16:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.47,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子同学摆出一副厌烦的神色 将收到的堆积如山的巧克力全退了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.61,0:16:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得那也算一种体贴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退回去了吗？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没法送给祥子大人巧克力吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也好好地享受节日如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是烦恼还是迷茫一定都会成为美好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去年只是一个旁观者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.68,0:17:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今年一定要创造能带去意大利的美好回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以佑巳同学也要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻宝那方面也加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.96,0:17:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.98,0:17:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也希望尽可能由最能理解我的人找到我的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.10,0:17:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说也许无法将巧克力送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次活动一定要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要最先找到红色的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为妹妹 我想成为最理解姐姐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.57,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 也许就能让祥子大人稍微认可我一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小刚狐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.26,0:18:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佑巳的美学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.01,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你都是趁大家不注意时\n悄悄地干完杂活才回去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得坐久了想干点什么而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有挑三捡四的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且向佑巳的自我满足上泼冷水也太不知趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.42,0:18:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错了什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.91,0:18:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得现在的佑巳总是在心里想突出自已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不太好说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.55,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我满足？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.91,0:18:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人在志愿校的考试中合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.30,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想第一个将此事告诉志摩子同学 才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要什么巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.46,0:19:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对白蔷薇姐妹来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.08,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必拘于形式 也能传达彼此的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 小刚狐不向我祝贺吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直没准备念大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.33,0:19:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应试复习也是从今年才开始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个月的复习就合格了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.08,0:19:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对还不知结果的江利子与蓉子很失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但从明天开始就可以好好地放松享受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人也要参加寻宝吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.81,0:19:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有趣的事怎么可以袖手旁观呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 至少得让你尖叫一声“嘎～”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵我就说过了吧 佑巳～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白蔷薇大人 请住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的眼神特别的严厉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当的开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才白蔷薇大人在这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.72,0:20:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有白蔷薇大人在你就会很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.96,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.30,0:20:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从什么时候开始 你变得讨厌我到连脸都不想看的程度呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.16,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么要避开我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开？ 怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.07,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是避开了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我还以为因为我是花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.63,0:20:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了公平地参加情人节企划才避开我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.52,0:20:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你却跟往常一样地接近令与志摩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.43,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使来到蔷薇馆 你也会在我来之前就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是要从我面前逃走似的避得远远的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早也是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在圣母玛莉亚之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像为了避开我似的走开了不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.56,0:21:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 今早有和祥子大人相遇过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.11,0:21:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也并没有特别去避开什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想说的话就好好地给我说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.80,0:21:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为我不想成为姐姐的妨碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才只做了扫除就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.03,0:21:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那不就是白蔷薇大人所说的自我满足吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你内心深处的话语为什么就不能向我倾诉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我什么都无法明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.89,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子 过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.56,0:22:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事 我都不可能会讨厌祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.81,0:22:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这些话无法说出口 却只换来泪水的流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.61,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的人的轮廓在眼前渐渐地模糊
